  "texts": [
    "Our system is deployed on the ARI humanoid robot, designed for use as a socially assistive companion (Cooper et al., 2020).",
    "ARI is 1.65m tall, has a mobile base, a touch-screen on the torso, movable arms to gesture, and a head with LCD eyes that enable gaze behaviour.",
    "A photo of ARI can be seen in Figure 1 and component (A) in Figure 2.",
    "It is equipped with a ReSpeaker Mic v2.0 array foot_2, an RGB camera (in the head), and a 180º fish-eye camera (in the chest) allowing us to capture and record the audio and video of the whole interaction from the robot's perspective.",
    "The robot verbalises given responses using Acapela Text-To-Speech foot_3."
  ],
